metadata.name: #01 - Deekay
metadata.description:
Our very first Bootyshaker and super saiyan artist is the dopest of the dope: DeeKay Kwon. He holds a very special place in our hearts because he hails from our little corner of the world: the commercial Motion Graphics and Animation industry. 

He builds tools, designs super appealing characters, and encourages positivity wherever he goes. DeeKayâ€™s art is smart, appealing, and happy. Extra ups from our team to see more Korean representation in the space as well. 

So here's to you, DeeKay. Cheers, and thank you for sharing yourself with the world!
